'''Conall Cernach'''

#(''Irish mythology'') A heroic warrior of the [[Ulaid]] in the [[Ulster Cycle]] of Irish mythology, who killed his [[second cousin]] [[Erc]].  Son of [[Amairgin mac Echit]] and [[Findchoem]].  Nephew of [[Conchobar mac Nessa]].  Cousin of [[Fedelm Noíchrothach]].

